<h2 id="view-consistency">View Consistency</h2>
<p>We use <a href="https://openai.com/blog/clip/">CLIPâ€™s</a> ability to jointly embed text and images to produce view-consistent and semantically meaningful stylizations over the entire 3D shape.</p>
